### Dashboard API-Football - leagues
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/dashboard/leagues

### Dashboard API-Football - seasons
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/dashboard/seasons

### Dashboard API-Football - teams by league & season
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/dashboard/teams?leagueId=128&season=2024

### Dashboard API-Football - players by team & season
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/dashboard/players?teamId=435&season=2024

### Dashboard API-Football - player rating in one fixture
GET http://127.0.0.1:3000/api/external/dashboard/player-rating?fixtureId=1208008&playerId=278
